# CreatorOS — environment setup index
#
# This repo uses per-app env files (not a single root .env).
#
# Local development
# -----------------
#   cp api/.env.example api/.env.local    # API + shared services config
#   cp web/.env.example web/.env.local    # Next.js dashboard
#
# Docker Compose (full stack)
# ---------------------------
#   cp api/.env.example api/.env
#   docker compose up --build
#   docker compose --profile hermes up --build   # + Ollama for Growth Coach
#
# Vercel + GitHub Actions (production)
# ------------------------------------
#   gh auth login
#   cp .github/env.production.example .github/env.production.local   # optional overrides
#   ./scripts/sync-github-env.sh --env production --repo YOUR_ORG/CreatorOS
#
#   GitHub secrets (manual): VERCEL_TOKEN, VERCEL_ORG_ID, VERCEL_PROJECT_ID
#
# Full guide: docs/DEPLOYMENT.md
#
# Variable reference
# ------------------
#   api/.env.example   — API, database, Redis, Celery, LLM, OAuth
#   web/.env.example   — NEXT_PUBLIC_* frontend vars
#   .github/env.manifest.json — GitHub secret vs variable mapping
